OL,3,CHow a state-of-the-art surgical robot
OL,4,Cis improving cancer care
OL,6,FLiverpool football legend Sir Kenny
OL,7,FDalglish and his wife Marina have
OL,8,Fhelped a hospital buy a high-tech
OL,9,Frobot to treat cancer patients.
OL,11,FThe #2 million robotic arm allows
OL,12,Fsurgeons to operate in the smallest of
OL,13,Fspaces - reducing the need for major
OL,14,Finvasive operations and could help
OL,15,Fspeed up recovery for head and neck
OL,16,Fcancer patients at Liverpool
OL,17,FUniversity Hospitals (LUHFT) in
OL,18,FFazakerley.
