OL,3,CHow a state-of-the-art surgical robot
OL,4,Cis improving cancer care
OL,6,FIt was paid for thanks in large part
OL,7,Fto a donation by the Marina Dalglish
OL,8,FAppeal (MDA), set up by the family in
OL,9,F2005 to support other cancer patients
OL,10,Fafter Marina was successfully treated
OL,11,Ffor breast cancer at Aintree in 2003.
OL,13,FThe million-pound donation was match
OL,14,Ffunded by the Hospital Trust and the
OL,15,Fnew device - called the Da Vinci
OL,16,FSingle Port (SP) surgical system - is
OL,17,Falready helping skilful surgeons treat
OL,18,Ftheir patients.
