OL,3,CHow a state-of-the-art surgical robot
OL,4,Cis improving cancer care
OL,6,FJason Fleming, Consultant Head and
OL,7,FNeck Surgeon at LUHFT, was the first
OL,8,FNHS consultant to operate the surgical
OL,9,Fsystem at Aintree.
OL,11,FHe said: "This next generation robot
OL,12,Fis really tailor made for operating
OL,13,Fthrough the mouth.
OL,15,F"So it's going to help us reach more
OL,16,Ftumours in difficult to reach areas of
OL,17,Fthe head and neck and therefore offer
OL,18,Fa minimally invasive surgical approach
OL,19,Fto more patients."
