OL,3,CHow a state-of-the-art surgical robot
OL,4,Cis improving cancer care
OL,6,FHe added: "Tumours of the throat
OL,7,F(tonsils and back of tongue) are
OL,8,Frising globally, but especially in
OL,9,FNorth West England, with smoking and
OL,10,Fhuman papillomavirus (HPV) exposure as
OL,11,Fmajor causes.
OL,13,F"In Liverpool we have a long record of
OL,14,Fpioneering minimally invasive surgery,
OL,15,Fbut now with the addition of the da
OL,16,FVinci SP, we will be able to offer the
OL,17,Flatest technology to a region with the
OL,18,Fgreatest need."
