OL,3,CHow a state-of-the-art surgical robot
OL,4,Cis improving cancer care
OL,6,FPatient Dave Pope, 65, from Frodsham
OL,7,Fin Cheshire, was one of the first to
OL,8,Fhave his tumour removed thanks to
OL,9,Fsurgery using the robot.
OL,11,FDave, who lives in Frodsham, said: "At
OL,12,Fthe first appointment in March with Mr
OL,13,FFleming, he told me about this new
OL,14,Frobot and that I'd be one of the first
OL,15,Fpatients to have surgery with it.
OL,17,F"If it helps more patients like me to
OL,18,Fbe seen and treated quickly, with
OL,19,Ffewer side effects and a faster
OL,20,Frecovery, it can only be a good thing.
