OL,3,CHow a state-of-the-art surgical robot
OL,4,Cis improving cancer care
OL,6,F"I'd urge anyone who is unsure about
OL,7,Ftheir symptoms or if you feel that
OL,8,Fsomething isn't as it should be, to go
OL,9,Fand get it checked out. Acting on your
OL,10,Fconcerns may be the best chance of an
OL,11,Fearly diagnosis."
